OL,5,G0300 Killer in the House: The Murders
OL,6,G     of Lesley Howell and Trevor
OL,7,G     Buchanan
OL,8,     FThis documentary examines the case
OL,9,     Fof one of the UK's most notorious
OL,10,     Fdouble killings. Colin Howell was
OL,11,     Fa married dentist with four
OL,12,     Fchildren and a pillar of the
OL,13,     FBaptist community in Coleraine,
OL,14,     Fbut was having an affair with
OL,15,     Fmarried Sunday school teacher
OL,16,     FHazel Buchanan. They agreed the
OL,17,     Fonly way they could be together
OL,18,     Fwas if they murdered their spouses
OL,19,     Fand Howell devised a plot to
OL,20,     Fpoison them with carbon monoxide
OL,21,     Ffumes and then stage their deaths
OL,22,     Fas a double suicide
